reviewText: All though I like the girls in all the Peach Dvds, I do like a little plot ever now and again and this was one of them. There is the normal strip tease thing but it's in between the story line. It's not the best story but they tried and I give them an A for effort. Good work Peach. Highly recommended for the Peach dvd lover and cute women lover too!

She was the whole reason I bought this.  I met her years ago when she was with WCW.  It's a Peach DVD with a story line that actually makes some sense.  This is supposed to be a sexy version of "9 to 5", with a little more revenge.  Oh, & LOTS of nudity & sexual situations.
Same quality you'd expect from Peach.
